2023 Ohio Entertainment Award Winner for Best New DJ 🔥🔥

To be honest this award means a lot to me. The last time i was awarded something was my acceptance letter into Morehouse College 10 years ago. I started Dj’ing in 2017 and i was just doing it because i wanted to learn how to operate everything when it’s comes to running a nightclub. Dj’ing was the second to last thing i had to scratch off my list. 

But becoming DJ Flavaz has completely change my life around and I’ve met all my idols, favorite artists, i dj infront of thousands of people,  network with many talents through my 6 years. I never looked at it as competition or a job. I’m really a raw as DJ and i give the vibes that people want!!! 

This year was hard and i was at my very low and it was times i didn’t wanna dj. But because off YALL, it kept me going. I felt the love and support everyone gave me. So i do wanna dedicate this award for my real supporters and fans. Thank Y’all, when i wanted to put the mic down y’all made me have to pick it right back up. 

Now i know that i can take DJ FLAVAZ further in life and i Promise this is only the beginning!!!! 

- Flavaz

Once you get out your comfort zone, success becomes easy. 

- More than just a DJ
